<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms of Service - <%= botConfig.name %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        /* Reuse same CSS variables from Privacy Policy for consistency */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #09090b;
            --accent: #FFD700;
            --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C00 0%, #FFD700 100%);
            --glass-bg: rgba(20, 20, 23, 0.7);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text-white: #ffffff;
            --text-gray: #a1a1aa;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-white);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .ambient-light { position: fixed; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1; }
        .orb { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(100px); opacity: 0.3; }
        .orb-1 { top: 50%; left: -10%; width: 50vw; height: 50vw; background: #8B0000; }
        .orb-2 { top: -10%; right: -10%; width: 40vw; height: 40vw; background: #FF8C00; }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .doc-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; background: var(--accent-gradient); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        h2 { color: var(--accent); margin: 30px 0 15px; font-size: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        p, li { color: var(--text-gray); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1rem; }
        ul { margin-left: 20px; }
        
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.1);
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Warning Box */
        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.05);
            border-left: 4px solid #ff4444;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .warning-title { color: #ff4444; font-weight: 700; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }

        .sidebar { position: sticky; top: 40px; height: fit-content; }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .action-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-invite { background: var(--accent-gradient); color: #000; }
        .btn-invite:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3); }

        .btn-home { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); color: #fff; }
        .btn-home:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

        .command-tag {
            background: #1e1e24;
            color: #FFD700;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .sidebar { position: relative; top: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="ambient-light">
        <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="doc-card">
            <span class="badge">Effective: January 15, 2026</span>
            <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
            <p>By inviting or using <strong><%= botConfig.name %></strong>, you agree to the following terms.</p>

            <h2><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> 1. Usage Agreement</h2>
            <p>ZarKos Ultimate is a utility, economy, and AI chat bot provided "as is". You agree not to use this bot to violate Discord's Community Guidelines or Terms of Service.</p>

            <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> 2. Liability & Responsibility</h2>
            <div class="warning-box">
                <span class="warning-title">IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER</span>
                We are <strong>NOT RESPONSIBLE</strong> for any damages or issues that occur in your server due to the misuse of bot commands by your admins or members.
            </div>
            <p>Specifically regarding commands like <span class="command-tag">/say</span> or <span class="command-tag">/embed</span>: These commands replicate user input. If a user abuses them, we cannot be held liable.</p>
            <p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> We strongly advise Server Owners to use the <span class="command-tag">/logsetup</span> command. This creates a secure log channel where the bot records exactly <em>who</em> used <em>what</em> command, ensuring accountability.</p>

            <h2><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 3. Economy System</h2>
            <p>ZarKos features a virtual economy system. Please note:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Virtual currency has <strong>NO real-world monetary value</strong>.</li>
                <li>We reserve the right to reset economy stats in case of bug abuse or critical updates (though we try to avoid this).</li>
            </ul>

            <h2><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> 4. Availability</h2>
            <p>ZarKos Ultimate was publicly launched on <strong>15.01.2026</strong>. While we aim for 99.9% uptime, we cannot guarantee uninterrupted service during maintenance or Discord API outages.</p>

            <div style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <p>Contact for Legal Inquiries: <a href="mailto:tuzhicodes@zohomail.in" style="color:#FFD700">tuzhicodes@zohomail.in</a></p>
                <p>YouTube: <a href="https://youtube.com/@TuZhiCodes" target="_blank" style="color:#FFD700">@TuZhiCodes</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #fff;">Bot Info</h3>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span style="color:var(--text-gray)">Version</span>
                    <span style="color:#fff">2.0 Ultimate</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <span style="color:var(--text-gray)">Type</span>
                    <span style="color:#FFD700">Utility / Econ / AI</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
                    <span style="color:var(--text-gray)">Dev</span>
                    <span style="color:#fff">TuZhi Codes</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #fff;">Get Started</h3>
                <a href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<%= botConfig.clientId %>&permissions=8&scope=bot%20applications.commands" target="_blank" class="action-btn btn-invite">
                    <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Add to Server
                </a>
                <a href="/" class="action-btn btn-home">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
